data.description: Buyer has an opportunity to assume seller's VA loan at 2.25%!!! Excellent condition home at the prime location of Magma Ranch backing up to a greenbelt, playground and community tennis courts! The open concept floorplan features a sizable great room, spacious kitchen with a large island, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The huge master bedroom boasts an spacious walk-in closet. New shower glass in Master bath. Plenty of storage places. Upgraded backyard with the paved patio, the young fruit trees and large pergola with misting system and sun curtains. RV gate&parking. Water softening system conveys. Just a short walk to the community park, playground, splash pad, and pool. 10 min walking to Magma Ranch K-8 school. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
